, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beth Potter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\"}, {\"begin\": 974, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9995452619454365, \"rank\": 0.0004549449324625151, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Taylor-Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Georgia Taylor-Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Taylor-Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Taylor-Brown\"}, {\"begin\": 1019, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.9983144750278425, \"rank\": 0.0016883707148207545, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final women's team member\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"world champion\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"the third woman\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic selection surprise picks?\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic selection surprise picks\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France and USA announce teams for Paris Coldwell, 29, (pictured above with Yee, Taylor-Brown and Dickinson as part of the gold-medal mixed relay team at the Commonwealth Games) was ranked four spots higher than Waugh, 25, in the Olympic ranking (eighth to 12th), and also finished ahead of Waugh at WTCS Cagliari in May, a race British Triathlon had declared would be a \\\"priority\\\" race.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1091, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9968990524000753, \"rank\": 0.0030972956931015223, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9885519538321462, \"rank\": 0.01134576637758545, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999557287548, \"rank\": 4.427129076594812e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Dickinson\", \"score\": 0.9995469784029725, \"rank\": 0.00045322691856870514, \"text\": \"Dickinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Dickinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Dickinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1422, \"end\": 1439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yee\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"Taylor-Brown\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold-medal mixed relay team\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"the Commonwealth Games\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"Waugh\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic ranking\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"12th\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"Waugh\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"WTCS Cagliari\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"priority\\\" race\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potter took third in Cagliari, while Taylor-Brown finished sixth, one spot ahead of Coldwell, with Waugh rounding out the top 10.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cagliari_Calcio\", \"score\": 0.9412694507052611, \"rank\": 0.06239504450986446, \"text\": \"Cagliari\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cagliari_Calcio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cagliari_Calcio\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Potter\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1487}, {\"ngram\": \"Taylor-Brown\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"Coldwell\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"Waugh\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were only 16 seconds separating the three women vying for the two available spots on the team.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only 16 seconds\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"the three women\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"the two available spots\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am disappointed, I am sad but above all I am angry at my federation,\\\" Coldwell wrote on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1804, \"end\": 1813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8071253572687185e-19, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my federation\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"Coldwell\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After the original selection was made, it became clear that I needed to appeal \\u2026 We then found out that we won the appeal, the arbitrator approved it on the grounds of 'failing to follow the selection policy.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the original selection\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"the appeal\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"the arbitrator\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"the grounds\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"the selection policy\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Based on the arbitrator's decision, Coldwell felt that she had a reasonable shot at being named to the team, but ultimately the panel stuck with its original decision.\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the arbitrator's decision\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"Coldwell\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"a reasonable shot\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"the panel\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"its original decision\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The panel would have to meet again, to redo selection and use their policy properly,\\\" Coldwell wrote.\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The panel\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"selection\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2251}, {\"ngram\": \"their policy\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"Coldwell\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew it would be an uphill battle to get them to admit they had made a mistake, but I thought a fair and competent panel would get it right.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2443, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an uphill battle\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"a fair and competent panel\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But no, still not enough.\\\"\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by \\ua731\\u1d0f\\u1d18\\u029c\\u026a\\u1d07 \\u1d04\\u1d0f\\u029f\\u1d05\\u1d21\\u1d07\\u029f\\u029f (@sophiecoldwell) After Coldwell's post and a number of angry comments to it, British Triathlon told a number of outlets (includingTri247andTriathlete)that it was an extremely difficult decision and that the event in Cagliari, while a priority event, was not a qualification race.\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2590, \"end\": 2607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2729, \"end\": 2737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cagliari_Calcio\", \"score\": 0.9412694507052611, \"rank\": 0.06239504450986446, \"text\": \"Cagliari\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43